  <div class="form-group col-sm-12">
    <%= f.label :weaponsBenefit, "4. There is a number of nuclear weapons sufficient to deter adversaries, regardless of the number of nuclear weapons they possess. Beyond that number, additional weapons provide little or no marginal benefit.", :class => "control-label" %><br>
    <%= f.radio_button :weaponsBenefit, "Strongly disagree" %> Strongly Disagree
    <%= f.radio_button :weaponsBenefit, "Disagree" %> Disagree
    <%= f.radio_button :weaponsBenefit, "Neither agree nor disagree" %> Neither agree nor disagree
    <%= f.radio_button :weaponsBenefit, "Agree" %> Agree
  </div>
  <div class="form-group col-sm-12">
    <%= f.label :superiorToRussia, "5. To maintain strategic stability, the U.S. nuclear arsenal does not have to be superior in number to Russia’s nuclear arsenal." %><br>
